    "120829392": {
      "title": "Best constants for sobolev inequalities for higher order fractional derivatives",
      "abstract": "We obtain sharp constants for Sobolev inequalities for higher order fractional derivatives. As an application, we give a new proof of a theorem of W. Beckner concerning conformally invariant higher-order differential operators on the sphere."
